的孩子们在父亲 72 岁生日之际向他致敬。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/robins-wish-documentary-robin-williams-2859119">《罗宾的愿望》：这部新纪录片告诉我们罗宾·威廉姆斯最后的日子</a></strong></li></ul><p>威廉姆斯于 2014 年自杀身亡，享年 63 岁。他有两个孩子，扎克和塞尔达。</p><p>扎克在社交媒体上向这位深受喜爱的已故演员致敬，写道：“72岁爸爸快乐！记得我曾经多么喜欢你的表情。</p><p> “你的朋友和亲人都非常熟悉那种顽皮而充满爱意的笑容。快乐、好奇、奇妙。想念你并永远爱你。”</p><p>塞尔达还向威廉姆斯致敬，分享了她父亲在 2007 年演员罢工中的照片，并表示随着美国演员工会演员和作家罢工的继续，他“今天和永远肯定会为艺术和艺术家而战”。</p><p>请参阅下面的帖子。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cu-5eLVrcMI/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 